# Byte-stability discipline, enforced at the git layer.
#
# Everything checks out with LF on every platform, so a Windows clone and a
# Linux clone hold identical bytes -- the demo's reproducible attestation
# ids depend on it. The golden artifacts are opted out of text handling
# entirely: they are byte-exact fixtures (tests compare them with
# read_bytes()), and any translation would be silent corruption.

* text=auto eol=lf
*.bat text eol=crlf
tests/golden/** -text
registry/approved.json -text
specs/*.json -text
